{"tid":88293,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"達哥：每天直播，失去娛樂、交際，食無定時身體消瘦，患上腸胃毛病","createTime":"2017-01-20T13:52:44.000Z","updateTime":"2017-01-21T06:30:55.000Z","uid":58099,"like":16,"dislike":13,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"dcd3832d30d1af0863fbe29fed9c748483897c02","tid":88293,"uid":58099,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-20T13:52:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://4.bp.blogspot.com/-1sxVn575QHQ/UNphvLoXgGI/AAAAAAAAflw/T2NZFO-3zEk/s1600/01-748410.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2F4.bp.blogspot.com%2F-1sxVn575QHQ%2FUNphvLoXgGI%2FAAAAAAAAflw%2FT2NZFO-3zEk%2Fs1600%2F01-748410.jpg&h=13515f91&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n做人都會想有娛樂，想有交際應酬，但是5年來為咗開台直播，我多年來堅持週一至週五每天直播兩小時，有時食無定時所以人都好消瘦，也落下了腸胃既毛病。我從來不喜歡賣慘，因為不想比負能量別人。但如果真係要論這些苦勞，當backup佬係1，我係9，但宜家係這些影片上既直接得益，佢係10，我係0，我都無說甚麼，為甚麼被指責的還是我？<br />\n<br />\n所以件事既原由就係咁。最後講句，每個人都會犯錯，但是，只有愚人才會執過不改。至於有些人說對我很失望，好抱歉，對你講既&ldquo;失望&rdquo;我無法再做甚麼了。"},{"pid":"903fb37eded5abc91a76a38286273578a0c013e3","tid":88293,"uid":58099,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-20T13:55:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c54bda146a94d2db3e10300f9b884d55478e9d6f","tid":88293,"uid":18948,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-20T13:56:17.000Z","msg":"Expedia<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5b3be0dd36053a2fb0599fd5eef4d5891e36afc2","tid":88293,"uid":58099,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-20T13:58:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f87bd89948615326a9b0fe0329789213b1fe6b87","tid":88293,"uid":3482,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-20T14:10:32.000Z","msg":"佢唔係一向都瘦底架咩 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" clas